# FILE: adminDashboard/adConsole/adConsole.desc
# ROLE: Global Ad-Injection & Traffic Controller
# ROUTE: /admin/ads
# ACCOUNT: Admin only — Business (Advertiser) accounts submit ad requests, Admin approves
# THEME: Dark · technical switchboard · zone map

## 1. GLOBAL TOGGLES
- ADS_ACTIVE: boolean toggle — kills all ads site-wide when false
- PROVIDER_MODE:
  - LOCAL_BANNERS: MongoDB-fetched custom ads from local businesses
  - GOOGLE_ADSENSE: auto-inject scripts (future)
  - HYBRID: both (zone-specific)

## 2. ZONE CONFIGURATION
- ZONE_HEADER: Dropdown [Local | Disabled]
- ZONE_SIDEBAR: Dropdown [Local | Disabled]
- ZONE_IN_FEED: Dropdown [Local | Disabled]
- VISUAL: small schematic map of the site showing which zones are "Live" (green) or "Dark" (muted)

## 3. LOCAL AD REPOSITORY (from Business Advertisers)
- SOURCE: Business accounts with businessType === 'advertiser' submit ad campaigns
- COLUMNS: Business Name · Ad Image · Target URL · Campaign Period · Status
- ADMIN ACTIONS: [✅ نشر] [❌ رفض] [📅 تمديد الفترة]
- CRUD for manually adding platform-owned banners

## 4. AD CARD DATA
- Image: WebP format, displayed as preview thumbnail
- Client Tag: "Elite Cafe" or "Halab Tech Store"
- Expiry Date: auto-deactivates on this date
- Clicks / Impressions counter

## 5. PERFORMANCE
- All ad nodes use Intersection Observer (lazy load)
- Disabled zones: container hidden — no DOM waste

## 6. CONNECTION TO BUSINESS ADVERTISER DASHBOARD
- Business (advertiser) submits campaign via /business/ads
- Appears here in "قيد المراجعة" queue for admin approval
- Once approved, goes live in selected zone
